{"id":366313,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/icon.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"班固米做菜人","groupHref":"/group/zuocai","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/43/4324.jpg?r=1574965416","message":"周末了 做了点儿芝麻花生酥糖 不知道大家小时候是否喜欢吃 <br>[img]<img src=\"https://s6.jpg.cm/2021/11/27/LLQ5fS.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt>[/img]<br>第一步  烤花生  用电饼铛 无油 中小火 烤大概10分钟 听到噼里啪啦声 基本就好啦<br><br>[img]<img src=\"https://s6.jpg.cm/2021/11/27/LLQ7ZW.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt>[/img]<br><br>第二步  将 烤好的花生 放凉 到 手触不烫手的温度 ,放入袋子,用擀面杖擀碎 本着节约粮食的原则 我保留了花生的外衣 <br>[img]<img src=\"https://s6.jpg.cm/2021/11/27/LLQlaL.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>第三步 放入适量熟芝麻  混合均匀<br><img src=\"https://s6.jpg.cm/2021/11/27/LLQ8rU.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>第四步 熬糖  蜂蜜和白糖混合   小火熬制成这个样子 <br><img src=\"https://s6.jpg.cm/2021/11/27/LLQVdf.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>第五步 把芝麻花生倒入糖稀 关火  快速搅拌均匀 <br><img src=\"https://s6.jpg.cm/2021/11/27/LLQepH.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br>第六步 把食材倒入模具整型 切割 <br><img src=\"https://s6.jpg.cm/2021/11/27/LLQdA2.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt>[/img]<br><br>具体材料配比:<br>没严格要求哈<br>我的配方是<br>250克花生<br>100克芝麻<br>50克凉水<br>100克蜂蜜<br>100克白砂糖 ","time":"2021-11-27 12:10","title":"芝麻花生酥糖","userId":"548418","userName":"安东篱","userSign":"(道同可言道)"}